## .gitignore for .NET / Blazor projects

# Ignore build outputs
**/bin/
**/obj/
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
artifacts/

# Visual Studio and editors
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/

# Rider
.idea/

# NuGet
*.nupkg
packages/

# User-specific files
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# Logs and test results
*.log
TestResults/
*.trx

# Dotnet WebAssembly / Blazor outputs
/wwwroot/_framework/
/wwwroot/service-worker-assets.js
/service-worker.published.js
/service-worker.js

# Misc
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
